On a random Wednesday , with zero measurements, no sewing machine, no plan and blind confidence I decided to cut up my old torn Kurti and somehow it became a top I actually want to wear (??) 
Yes, the edges are still rough. Yes, the stitching might betray me at any moment. But, pretty sure my younger self would be proud of this little experiment. ✂️❤️😋
